            or need support, our team is here to help.
        </p>
    </div>

    
    <div class="row g-4">
        
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <div class="card shadow-sm h-100">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h4 class="card-title mb-3">Get in Touch</h4>
                    <p class="card-text text-muted">
                        Reach out to us using the contact details below. We respond
                        within 24 hours on business days.
                    </p>

                    <ul class="list-unstyled">
                        <li class="mb-2">
                            <strong>Email:</strong>
                            <span class="text-primary"> support@example.com</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="mb-2">
                            <strong>Phone:</strong>
                            +1 234 567 890
                        </li>
                        <li class="mb-2">
